verbose_text: Patients were categorized as deficient in the following micronutrients according to our hospital trust guidelines and cut-off measurements : * Serum ferritin levels < 20 mmol/L * Serum folate levels < 3 mmol/L * Serum vitamin D levels < 25 mmol/L * Serum vitamin B12 levels < 180 mmol/L 2.4 Statistical analyses.
